headline: Terex Q1 Earnings & Revenues Beat Estimates, Decline Y/Y on Low Volumes
summary: TEX witnesses year-over-year decline in Q1 earnings due to low volumes. Its guidance for 2025 earnings per share of $4.70 - $5.10 suggests a 20% decline at the midpoint.

headline: 1 Dow Jones Stock with Impressive Fundamentals and 2 to Be Wary Of
summary: The Dow Jones (^DJI) is made up of 30 of the most established and influential companies in the market. But even blue-chip stocks can struggle - some are dealing with slowing growth, outdated business models, or increasing competition.
